{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":75,"Text":"我必以星宿的沒落處盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":76,"Text":"這確是一個重大的盟誓，假若你們知道。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":77,"Text":"這確是寶貴的《古蘭經》，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":78,"Text":"記錄在珍藏的經本中，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":79,"Text":"只有純潔者才得撫摸那經本。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":80,"Text":"《古蘭經》是從全世界的主降示的。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":81,"Text":"難道你們藐視這訓辭，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":82,"Text":"而以否認代替感謝嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":83,"Text":"（你們）怎麼不在靈魂到將死者的咽喉的時候——"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":84,"Text":"那時候，你們大家看著他，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":85,"Text":"我比你們更臨近他，但你們不曉得，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":86,"Text":"如果你們不是受報應的，——"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":87,"Text":"你們怎不使靈魂復返於本位呢？如果你們是說實話的。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":88,"Text":"如果他是被眷顧的，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":89,"Text":"那末，他將享受舒適、給養與恩澤的樂園；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":90,"Text":"如果他是幸福者，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":91,"Text":"那末，一般幸福的人將對他說：「祝你平安！」"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":92,"Text":"如果他是迷誤的、否認復活者，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":93,"Text":"那末，他將享受沸水的款待，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":94,"Text":"和烈火的燒灼。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":95,"Text":"這確是無可置疑的真理。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":96,"Text":"故你應當頌揚你的主的大名。"}]}